Psalm 19/XX/PR

/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. Rabbi Kaplan used to say that if you want to discover the
truth of a statement about God, you must invert it. He would then state,
"The Torah of God is flawless, restoring the soul" should be read
"whatever restores the soul is the Torah of God."    /SC/XXM.S./XX/PR

